This repository serves as a template for Angular monorepo projects.

## Quick Start for New Project

1. Edit `project.config.js` with client information
2. Run `npm install && npm run configure`
3. Test with `npm run build:all`
4. See docs/TEMPLATE.md for complete guide

## Template Includes

- Angular 19 monorepo (3 projects)
- Tailwind CSS v3
- SCSS architecture (variables, mixins, functions)
- CI/CD pipelines (GitHub Actions)
- Docker support
- Commitlint + Husky
- Branch protection ready
- Environment management
- Public assets folder (Angular 18+ convention)

